http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Hyderabad/CM-pays-homage-to-martyrs/article14022203.ece

Chief Minister K. Chandrasekhar Rao laid a wreath at the Veerula Sainika Smarak (War Memorial) and paid homage to the martyrs at the Army Parade Grounds in Secunderabad here on Tuesday.Senior officers of the tri-forces and veterans also laid the wreaths at the War Memorial.A large number of serving and retired officers of three services were present on the occasion.Wreath-laying ceremony is organised by the headquarters of Telangana and Andhra Sub-Area every year on the occasion of Republic Day at War Memorial in Secunderabad, as a mark of respect and to pay homage to the valiant soldiers who laid their lives to uphold the honour and pride of the country.